{
  "stem": "56.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Voik-- ?] the [? friends ?] who went to beat up the Jews in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] seeing who it was, I just didn't pay any attention to-- to what I heard, because it couldn't be [?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Voik. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he says, where is your father?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where is your mother?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where do you live?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he picked me up, put me and his shoulders, and he says, direct me to your home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was about, like, half a block down the street where we lived.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I brought him home, and he walked in, and he saw my mother in bed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So first thing he did, he was-- he grabbed her, he was holding her and dancing with her.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he started yelling at my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "How come you didn't come to see me?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "How could you let her get so sick?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father says, what are you talking about?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "How could I come to see you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he proceeded to tell my father that he's now the head of the criminal police in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, we heard about the criminal police-- we all knew about it, that once someone was taken to the criminal police, you never heard or saw him anymore.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You did hear screams coming out of there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew that terrible things were going on there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] immediately, he told my father, you come and see me, and I'll take care of you.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he spent some times with us, telling stories about his wife, who was my sister's girlfriend, and about the baby that he has.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at the same time, he wanted to know all about us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then he left.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
